  "description": "<p><strong>微软CEO史蒂夫鲍尔默终于承认，微软造了太多Surface平板，而且Windows设备的销量并不如微软预期得那么好。</strong>来自国外媒体的内线消息，在本周早前的微软内部会议上，鲍尔 默与微软COO（首席运营官）Kevin Turner都提到了最近Surface RT令微软亏损9亿美元和Windows不同设备销售速度的问题。此外，鲍尔默也很直接地谈到了为Windows Phone争取Instagram，以及对下一代Surface的计划。</p><img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cnbeta.feedsportal.com/c/34306/f/624776/s/2f31b738/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /><div class=\"mf-viral\"><table border=\"0\"><tr><td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F246188.htm&amp;t=%E9%B2%8D%E5%B0%94%E9%BB%98%E6%89%BF%E8%AE%A4%EF%BC%9ASurface+RT%E9%80%A0%E5%BE%97%E5%A4%AA%E5%A4%9A+Windows%E8%AE%BE%E5%A4%87%E9%94%80%E9%87%8F%E4%B8%8D%E5%8F%8A%E9%A2%84%E6%9C%9F\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F246188.htm&amp;t=%E9%B2%8D%E5%B0%94%E9%BB%98%E6%89%BF%E8%AE%A4%EF%BC%9ASurface+RT%E9%80%A0%E5%BE%97%E5%A4%AA%E5%A4%9A+Windows%E8%AE%BE%E5%A4%87%E9%94%80%E9%87%8F%E4%B8%8D%E5%8F%8A%E9%A2%84%E6%9C%9F\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F246188.htm&amp;t=%E9%B2%8D%E5%B0%94%E9%BB%98%E6%89%BF%E8%AE%A4%EF%BC%9ASurface+RT%E9%80%A0%E5%BE%97%E5%A4%AA%E5%A4%9A+Windows%E8%AE%BE%E5%A4%87%E9%94%80%E9%87%8F%E4%B8%8D%E5%8F%8A%E9%A2%84%E6%9C%9F\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gplus/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F246188.htm&amp;t=%E9%B2%8D%E5%B0%94%E9%BB%98%E6%89%BF%E8%AE%A4%EF%BC%9ASurface+RT%E9%80%A0%E5%BE%97%E5%A4%AA%E5%A4%9A+Windows%E8%AE%BE%E5%A4%87%E9%94%80%E9%87%8F%E4%B8%8D%E5%8F%8A%E9%A2%84%E6%9C%9F\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.fe